The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Nation | Minister dead
                                                                                                               Minister dead
                            
	Chandigarh, March 29 (PTI): Punjab minister and senior Akali leader Kanwaljit Singh was today killed when two trucks crashed into his car near Chandigarh.        
	The 67-year-old general secretary of the Akali Dal was coming back from Ludhiana. The government has ordered an inquiry into the incident.                                                                                                                                                                           
